{"tid":1506524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[護旗手在哪]唔係政府出新聞稿我都唔知琴日支國旗又俾人搞","createTime":"2019-08-25T23:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:35:25.000Z","uid":66260,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16dfae9daa1b1bad1ab306cd2080c89f6b4ced41","tid":1506524,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:31:02.000Z","msg":"唔睇廢話睇重點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">政府回應暴力示威活動<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n　　政府發言人就昨日（八月二十五日）在葵青及荃灣等地區的示威活動作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n　　昨日在葵青及荃灣進行的遊行集會，雖然警方經與主辦方協商後已發出不反對通知書，但有示威者在遊行期間偏離原定路線，堵塞道路，與警方對峙，以磚塊、鐵枝等肆意襲擊警務人員，並向警車和警務人員多次投擲汽油彈，嚴重破壞社會安寧，對在場執法的警務人員和市民的人身安全構成極大的威脅。</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有示威者在集會地點葵涌運動場取下國旗，並肆意踐踏，行為挑戰國家權威</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">，亦涉嫌觸犯《國旗及國徽條例》。晚上一批激進示威者以暴力破壞多間位於荃灣的商舖，到場處理的警務人員一度被多名暴徒襲擊，在生命受到威脅的情況下曾向天鳴槍示警。之後激進示威者的暴力行動蔓延至深水埗、尖沙咀及紅隧九龍出入口等多個地點。<br />\n<br />\n　　激進示威者升級的違法及暴力行為不但令人髮指，更將香港推向極為危險的邊緣，特區政府予以嚴厲譴責，警方亦會嚴正追究。特區政府呼籲廣大市民共同打擊暴力，維護法治，盡快回復社會秩序。 <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月26日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間0時47分</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/26/P2019082600031.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F26%2FP2019082600031.htm&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=03635e54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/26/P2019082600031.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n每次見到支匪旗俾人侮辱完然後班黨媒嬲嬲豬個樣我就好心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddefddaf0a96fd9eb0a8901034dd5ac058b4a20","tid":1506524,"uid":25108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:35:42.000Z","msg":"一塊布每次都可以激嬲14億人"},{"pid":"c0abe49f348033f78f01c798cb64621009056402","tid":1506524,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:39:02.000Z","msg":"但唔見有圖"},{"pid":"f6c68f36068c6a734ebeb5725e6b1e1be562359b","tid":1506524,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0abe49f348033f78f01c798cb64621009056402","tid":1506524,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:39:02.000Z","msg":"但唔見有圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:40:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190825/mobile/bkn-20190825154224455-0825_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190825%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190825154224455-0825_00822_001.html&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f966fd41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190825/mobile/bkn-20190825154224455-0825_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0c659193954841619e977ae239d29234c3248e","tid":1506524,"uid":168717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:44:23.000Z","msg":"的士佬果班都有做wo 做咩唔出黎 廢up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448ab0ef5aed83daea5a39476eb665014da192d1","tid":1506524,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"「圖」多個內地日文Twitter帳號惡意抹黑示威 並大量宣傳解放軍資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}